					&lt;blockquote&gt;
					  &lt;p&gt;Sauvignon Blanc, Chardonnay and sweet wines like Moscato are best
					  served after 20 minutes after pulling from the refrigerator&lt;/p&gt;
					&lt;/blockquote&gt;

					&lt;p&gt;So keep the wine chilled and remove and let it stand before serving &lt;/p&gt;

					&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.sutterhome.com/wine-and-life-blog/our-wines-entertaining-wine-%26-food/wine-101-wine-temperature#" rel="nofollow"&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

