				<Text Type="text">
					&lt;p&gt;In Brazil, we have some festivities on July, and in this period it's common to drink warm and hot wine, pure, or with some fruits and spices. It's called "quentão" and is usually made with cubes of apple and cinnamon. &lt;/p&gt;

